    <briefdescription>
<para>Integer-only variant of <ref refid="classamrex_1_1Parser" kindref="compound">amrex::Parser</ref>. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="classamrex_1_1IParser" kindref="compound">IParser</ref> parses expressions composed of integer literals, integer variables, and integer-returning functions. It emits executors that evaluate to long long on host or GPU. </para>
